snippet.title: DEEPSPACE Beta Release Trailer
snippet.description:
DEEPSPACE (DPS) is a leading exploration strategy multi-chain Web3 blockchain game combining elements of turn-based strategy and real-time first-person gameplay set in an expansive space-based universe where players can trade and upgrade spaceships, explore, mine for resources, and battle AI opponents and other players. The project brings multiple proprietary innovations to the web3 gaming industry

We're on Ethereum and BNB Chain.  Buy our native token DEEPSPACE (DPS) on Uniswap or our dapp to start your adventure.

Come and make a name for yourself in DEEPSPACE!

---------------------------
▶️ For more on DEEPSPACE & to play: https://deepspace.game
